issue.title: PHP-DI 7.0
issue.body:
This pull request contains a possible v7.0 version.

Changes:

- support PHP 8.0 and up
- #769 Allow `new Container()` with definitions
- #738, #741 support PHP 8 attributes for injections: welcome `#[Inject]` to replace `@Inject`!
- drop support for `@Inject` used with phpdoc annotations -> only native PHP types are supported now
    That makes PHP-DI simpler, faster and lighter (no need for the PhpDocReader package)
- typed everything that can be typed
- PSR-11 1.2 and 2.0 support

TODO:

- [x] #718 
- [x] #812 

Blocked by:

- [x] https://github.com/opis/closure/pull/67
- [x] https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/4702

comment.body: FWIW I have a fairly extensive Container test suite that's been utilizing `v7.x-dev` with 8.1 for quite some time and everything has worked great.

release.body:
## What's Changed
* adjust version to dev-main by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/177
* Feature/logging by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/187
* Ensure delegate abstract services no aliased by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/188
* Include correct alias reason for multiple primary by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/189
* Make sure we log bootstrapped container factory by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/190
* Fix reference to Fixtures by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/191
* Add third-party services first by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/193
* Improve logging multiline values by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/197
* Improve start/end lifecycle logging, fixes #195 by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/199
* Make sure build command logs by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/201
* Exclude profile for Bootstrap logging by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/202


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v1.3.0...v1.4.0
